| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2371 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b4d08f64-c83a-525b-a6a2-14d19fe4b9b0"
